2026-05-16T19:47:07.3292141Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3292967Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3293861Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3294602Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3295451Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3296270Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3297053Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T19:47:07.3297737Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
